{"body":"Citation, commencement and extent 1 1 These Regulations may be cited as the Data Protection, Privacy and Electronic Communications (Amendments etc) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019. 2 Subject to paragraph (3), they come into force on exit day. 3 Regulations 7 and 8 and Schedule 4 come into force on 29th March 2019. 4 An amendment, repeal or revocation made by these Regulations has the same extent in the United Kingdom as the provision to which it relates.","citation_label":"S.I. 2019/419 reg. 1","citation_path":"uk/regulation/uksi/2019/419/1","document_class":"regulation","expression_date":"2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments","heading":"Regulation 1","id":"4a087482-4fd0-5d64-b108-2d8ea65f10ac","identifiers":{"legislation.gov.uk:number":"419","legislation.gov.uk:provision":"1","legislation.gov.uk:type":"uksi","legislation.gov.uk:year":"2019"},"jurisdiction":"uk","kind":"regulation","language":"en","legal_identifier":"S.I. 2019/419 reg. 1","level":1,"metadata":{"extent":["E","W","S","N.I."],"retrieved_at":"2026-07-03"},"ordinal":1,"parent_citation_path":"uk/regulation/uksi/2019/419","parent_id":"d0724376-ca00-5c87-a6c1-287b86bf6aa9","source_as_of":"2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments","source_document_id":"uksi/2019/419","source_format":"legislation.gov.uk-clml","source_id":"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/made","source_path":"sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments/uksi/2019/419/regulation-1.xml","source_url":"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/regulation/1/made","version":"2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments"}
{"body":"Part 6 (enforcement) (other than Schedules 15 to 17) 64 1 Section 157 is amended as follows. 2 In subsection (1), for “GDPR” (in both places) substitute “UK GDPR”; 3 In subsection (2)(a), omit “74,”. 4 In subsection (5), for “20 million Euros” (in both places) substitute “£17,500,000”. 5 In subsection (6), for “10 million Euros” (in both places) substitute “£8,700,000”. 6 Omit subsection (7).","citation_label":"S.I. 2019/419 Sch. 2 para. 64","citation_path":"uk/regulation/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/64","document_class":"regulation","expression_date":"2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments","heading":"Schedule 2 paragraph 64","id":"af65871b-3d4e-5df6-8cde-b7ebe700efcd","identifiers":{"legislation.gov.uk:number":"419","legislation.gov.uk:provision":"64","legislation.gov.uk:type":"uksi","legislation.gov.uk:year":"2019"},"jurisdiction":"uk","kind":"paragraph","language":"en","legal_identifier":"S.I. 2019/419 Sch. 2 para. 64","level":1,"metadata":{"extent":["E","W","S","N.I."],"retrieved_at":"2026-07-03"},"ordinal":1,"parent_citation_path":"uk/regulation/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2","parent_id":"6371f44e-459b-58e2-8802-086b055bcbb4","source_as_of":"2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments","source_document_id":"uksi/2019/419","source_format":"legislation.gov.uk-clml","source_id":"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/made","source_path":"sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments/uksi/2019/419/schedule-2-paragraph-64.xml","source_url":"https://www.legislation.gov.uk/uksi/2019/419/schedule/2/paragraph/64/made","version":"2026-07-03-uk-dpa-penalty-cap-amendments"}
